# Web app env. In LOCAL DEV you do NOT need this file: next.config.mjs auto-loads
# the repo-root .env for any unset keys. Copy ../.env.example to ../.env and fill it.
# Use web/.env.local only to OVERRIDE a value just for the web app (e.g. point the
# dashboard at the deployed API instead of a local one):
#
#   CALMA_API_URL=https://calma-api-wheat.vercel.app
#
# Keys the dashboard reads (all live in the repo-root .env): WORKOS_CLIENT_ID,
# WORKOS_API_KEY, WORKOS_COOKIE_PASSWORD, NEXT_PUBLIC_WORKOS_REDIRECT_URI,
# CALMA_API_URL, CALMA_SERVICE_TOKEN, DASHBOARD_DEV_TENANT_ID.
